# Bulky generated intermediates from the phase pipelines.
# Rule of thumb: keep the *_top3/ deliverable renders and the JSON/CSV/JSONL
# metrics+trace (small, needed for the report); ignore the full per-candidate
# image dumps and the _warm/ / _dupes/ scratch renders.
outputs/phase3/
outputs/phase4/
# ...but never ignore the small top-3 deliverable folders.
!outputs/phase4_top3/
!outputs/phase4_s*_top3/
